reply_text:
@extrusdnterre1485 It great as long as you are a newcomer. If you know the lore of the games then you will notice how the show needlesly bastardized at least half of it so it could use it for it's political agenda.
They really did nail Dante's character however, which was my biggest concern regarding the show, so it get's a pass from me.
The political and anti religion crap was very annoying however.
